&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.aws.amazon.com/zh_cn/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/t2-credits-baseline-concepts.html&#34;&gt;CPU 积分和基准性能 - Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
